# =============================================================================
# TEMPLATE TRAE AI - ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES
# =============================================================================
# 
# ⚠️  WARNING: NEVER COMMIT ACTUAL CREDENTIALS TO VERSION CONTROL
# 
# This file contains example/placeholder values only. Before deploying to
